Vanilla flags
=============

Goal: change the default

Flag group V for vanilla:
 - Vs - keep shop glitch
 - Vt - don't shuffle mimics
 - Rg - route glitches into logic

Remove all F flags, keep the G flags

Add a * subflag:
 - G* would be "all glitches on"
 - automatically collapse?
 - single canonical rep for any given flagset


